name: Ai-LLOWEEN // Crossover - 5# Suryah of the East
description:
Suryah of the East - A mercenary from the distant Eastern lands. 
Bad news travels fast and the struggles of Rosenburg were no exception. Glory-seeking warriors came from all corners of the world, but few made a name quite like Suryah.
Not a lot is known about him besides the fact that he is agile and an expert in the blade arts. 
He wields his strange thin, and long eastern sword with ease. 
Some say they saw him slice 2 vampires in half with one single swop! 
Rosenburg could do with a few more warriors like him...
